Deal or No Deal Island: A guide to watch as the series marks its premiere

etimes.in / Feb 27, 2024, 12:36 (IST)

Hosted by Joe Manganiello, 'Deal or No Deal Island' is a spin-off series where 13 contestants compete on the banker's private island to uncover hidden briefcases with over $200 million. They face challenges, make strategic decisions, and aim for a lucrative deal. Premieres on February 26, 2024, on NBC and Fubo.
